list.comment: Work towards fully web-container compatible version now ~80% done! Environment-Variable "GERMANER_HOME" required. This is the place to put the data.zip and properties file. (IMPORTANT NOTE: at the moment the build germaner-with-dependencies.jar is still the 2015 version from the respective maven repository; therefore the classes [GermaNERMain.class, NERReader.class, CrfSuiteWrapper.class] need to be added/replaced manually from germanner.jar to germanner-with-dependencies.jar before a fix in the pom.xml can be implemented!)
